### Add a new example app (Next.js)

- **Create the app**:

```bash
cd examples
pnpm dlx create-next-app@latest <example-name> --use-pnpm --ts --eslint --src-dir --app --import-alias "@/*"
```

- **Sync dependencies with the catalog**:

```bash
pnpm sync-versions
```

- **Delete the nested lockfile and workspace file if exists**:

```bash
pnpm install
```
